data.meta_description: Download Image of Prince of Jordan Faisal Bin Al-Hussein, Gen. Lloyd. Free for commercial use, no attribution required. Prince of Jordan Faisal Bin Al-Hussein, Gen. Lloyd Austin, commander, U.S. Central Command, Lt. Gen. James L. Terry, commander, U.S. Army Central, and Jordanian Chief of Staff Lt. Gen. Mashal Zaben observe the Combined Armed Live Fire Exercise (CALFEX) demonstration in Jebel Petra, Jordan, June 5, in support of Exercise Eager Lion 2014. Eager Lion is a recurring, multinational exercise designed to strengthen military-to-military relationships, increase interoperability between partner nations and enhance regional security and stability.. Dated: 05.06.2014.
